title: RTN Base Stations
description: Iowa DOT's Real-Time Network Base Stations.Visit the?Real-Time Network homepage?for more information.

title: RWIS - Surface Data
description: Live surface/pavement data from Roadway Weather Information System (RWIS) sites in Iowa. Any field of NA or 9999 describes an invalid value being sent from sensor and was excluded for this REST service. This data gets updated every 10 minutes.

title: RWIS - Traffic Data
description: Live traffic data from Roadway Weather Information System (RWIS) sites in Iowa. Any field of NA or 9999 describes an invalid value being sent from sensor and was excluded for this REST service. This data gets updated every 10 minutes.

title: Deer Kill FY 2008
description: This database is a yearly snapshot of deer kill sites as entered by Maintenance field crews. These records are generated from a view that comes from the Maintenance Resource Management System. The data is input from the field staff who are responsible for removal of the deer from the roadway.?This does not necessarily correlate to crash data related to deer impacts; this is strictly deer downed within the right of way that are documented and moved by Maintenance staff.

title: RWIS - Deep Probe Data
description: Live Deep Probe data from Roadway Weather Information System (RWIS) sites in Iowa. Any field of NA or 9999 describes an invalid value being sent from sensor and was excluded for this REST service. This data gets updated every 10 minutes.

title: RAMS - Right Shoulder Curbed
description: Right Shoulder Curbed data maintained inside the Roadway Asset Management System (RAMS).

title: AWOS Data
description: Live Automated Weather Observing System (AWOS) data pulled from NOAA METAR GeoJSON Feed for Iowa AWOS sites.
